    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "I looked at the test data in CI and interestingly this test averages very fast, despite the comments in the code saying otherwise. \r\n<img width=\"943\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/coder/coder/assets/19379394/a6ee174f-7da6-4474-af5c-621a628724d9\">\r\n\r\nThat being said, I still think if we are timing out at 50 seconds something on the CI box is running out of resources, and moving this to the database will still reduce the test startup burden for this test. ",
